                                    </div>
                                    <div class="bookingBox flexBox">
                                        <div class="det">
                                            <ul class="countList short">
                                                <li>The new student in the housing fills out the housing contract and
                                                    signs it.
                                                </li>
                                                <li>Pay the full year's fees or at least six months' fees.</li>
                                                <li>Bring a 4*6 personal photo.</li>
                                                <li>A copy of the ID card if he is Yemeni.</li>
                                                <li>A copy of the passport if he is not Yemeni.</li>
                                                <li>If the old student in the residence wishes to renew the reservation
                                                    for the new year, he must fill out the residence reservation form.
                                                </li>
                                                <li>Upon his return from travel, he pays the fees he owes.</li>
                                                <li>Payment of fees is made through the college accountants.</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="img">
